snippet.title: Johanna Hedva - 'GLUT: a superabundance of nothing' (2021) gameplay with ASL
snippet.description: Johanna Hedva created GLUT as part of their 2021 Adam Reynolds Award. GLUT went on to inspire the four artworks in the 2021-22 ARA Shortlist Exhibition, Empty When Full. You can play GLUT at glut.website and you can visit the full Empty When Full exhibition is www.emptywhenfull.co.uk.
